headline: Target Hospitality Announces Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call Schedule
summary: Target Hospitality Corp. ("Target Hospitality", "Target" or the "Company") (NASDAQ: TH), one of North America's largest providers of vertically integrated modular accommodations and value-added hospitality services, today announced that it will release its second quarter 2025 financial results before the market opens on Thursday, August 7, 2025. The Company has also scheduled a conference call for Thursday, August 7, 2025, at 9:00 am Eastern Time (8:00 am Central Time) to discuss the results.
